# --- Heavy mounted-at-runtime data (provided via volumes in docker-compose) ---
**/chrome_profile/
# Host CfT binaries (win64) — Linux image downloads its own linux64 CfT at build
**/chrome-for-testing/
**/*.db
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3
**/*.db-journal
**/*.db-wal
**/*.db-shm

# --- Offline tuning / training code (not used by the API runtime) ---
MultiagentSystem/agents_tuners/

# --- Build artefacts / runtime logs not needed in image ---
**/*.log
**/*.log.*
MultiagentSystem/predictions_results*.csv
MultiagentSystem/confusion_matrix.png
Logs/available_features.json

# --- Pre-computed agent output artefacts (overwritten at runtime) ---
MultiagentSystem/agents/news_analyser/news_archive.json
MultiagentSystem/agents/news_analyser/news_predict.json
MultiagentSystem/agents/economic_calendar_analyser/calendar_predict.json
MultiagentSystem/agents/onchain_indicators/input_data.json
MultiagentSystem/agents/onchain_indicators/onchain_predict.json
